Label: Data Classification
Default:
if (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Supplier_DataExchange> = "n") then "No Data Held"
else If(
      (Intersects(("device"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("web", "geo", "text"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Devise_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("education"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("k8"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Education_Student_Info_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("employment"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("cc", "welfare"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Employment_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("financial"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("cc", "cardholder", "bank"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Financial_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("gov", "medical"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("business"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("contract"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Product_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("tech"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("creds", "stores", "pin", "question", "response", "key", "certs"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Technical_List>)))
 or (Intersects(("other"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("ethnicity", "race", "religion", "beliefs", "politics", "union", "sex", "background", "birth", "child", "content", "other"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Other_List>))) 
)Then "Restricted"    
Else if (
       (Intersects(("contact", "device", "education","employment","financial","tech","other"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("business"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("product", "recovery", "systems", "security", "procedures", "emails"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Product_List>))) 
) Then "Confidential"  
Else if (
Intersects(("business"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>))
) Then "Internal" 
Else "Public"

Label: Payment Card Information (PCI)
Personal Information (PI)
Default:
if (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Supplier_DataExchange> = "n") then "n"
else If(
    (Intersects(("contact", "other", "education", "financial", "gov", "medical"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("device"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("web", "search", "tags", "id", "likes", "geo", "device", "data", "text"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Devise_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("employment"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("income", "retire", "welfare", "emergency", "dependent"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Employment_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("business"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("emails"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Product_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("tech"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("creds", "response"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Technical_List>))) 
)Then "PI" 
Else If (<Supplier_Is_Legacy> <> "y" and <WESTERNDIGITAL_Supplier_Expedite> <> "y") Then "n"

 or (Intersects(("employment"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("id"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Employment_List>))) 
 or (Intersects(("gov"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List>)) and Intersects(("ssn", "national", "driverslic", "birth", "tin", "passport", "military", "tribal"), (<WESTERNDIGITAL_Data_Class_List_Government_List>)))

Label:
Compliance Certification</br></br>
Applicant, on behalf of itself and its employees, shareholders, directors, and agents, declares as follows:</br></br>
Conduct: Our Company is committed to advancing its corporate social and environmental responsibility (CSER) within our internal operations and with our global suppliers. We are an active member of the Responsible Business Alliance (RBA) and subscribe to the RBA Code of Conduct. This means that weve made a commitment that our supply chains are safe, that workers are treated with respect and dignity, and that business operations are environmentally responsible and conducted ethically.</br></br>
We expect those who provide goods and services to us (our suppliers) to operate ethically and responsibly while working with us. By submitting your forms to our Company and by continuing to work with our Company, you agree to operate ethically and responsibly.</br></br>
We understand that not all provisions of the RBA Code of Conduct will apply to all suppliers. For example, the RBAs environmental standards around hazardous substances may not apply to software or marketing service providers, but the RBAs ethics standards apply to all of our suppliers. We also understand that not all of our suppliers may be members of the RBA, and further recognize that you may have your own Code of Conduct on which you train your employees.</br></br>
However, to the extent that any provision in the RBA Code of Conduct relates to goods or services you are providing to our Company, we expect that you operate in compliance with the relevant principles outlined in the RBA Code of Conduct, our Global Code of Conduct, our Corporate Responsibility Guidelines and our Supplier Code of Conduct.</br></br>
For global production parts suppliers and contract manufacturers that support the manufacture of our Company's products (including WD and other brands), our Responsible Supply Chain webpage outlines additional requirements.</br></br>
Refer to the following links:
[Global Code of Conduct](https://documents.westerndigital.com/content/dam/doc-library/en_us/assets/public/western-digital/collateral/company/western-digital-global-code-of-conduct.pdf), [Corporate Responsibility Guidelines](https://www.westerndigital.com/company/corporate-sustainability/business-integrity-ethics), [Responsible Supply Chain](https://www.wdc.com/about-wd/global-citizenship/responsible-supply-chain.html), [Western Digital Supplier Code of Conduct](https://documents.westerndigital.com/content/dam/doc-library/en_us/assets/public/western-digital/collateral/company/western-digital-supplier-code-of-conduct.pdf)
Please confirm that you have read, understood, and acknowledged the above (Code of Conduct)

Name: Bank Account Discrepancy
Description: Reviews and resolves cases where a suppliers bank account name does not match their legal or DBA name, determining if the account can be approved or requires changes

Name: Flagged Country Review
Description: Users in this group must review the invitation prior to it being sent to the supplier when the expected country of registration or the countries where products/services will be provided match any of the high risk countries

Name: Final Connect Approval
Description: Final approval of a supplier during the "Connect" phase before completing the supplier connection

Name: Final Invite Approval
Description: Final approval of an invitation in the "Invite" phase before a connection request is sent to a supplier

Name: Final Review Approval
Description: Final approval of a supplier response during the "Review" phase before connecting to a supplier

Name: Non-Network Approval
Description: Users in this group will approve a Non-Network Request before the supplier is created.

Name: Non-Network Requests
Description: Users in this group have the ability to create and manage Non-Network (Proxy) supplier records

Name: TPMO Governance
Description: Users in this group are assigned an approval task when any risk domain is identified as High risk

Name: W8 Review
Description: Users in this group will be notified and a task created whenever a W8 is added or updated

Name: WDC-ABAC
Description: Set by Savyint: Correlates to the ABAC RDOs, which includes the Ethics & Integrity topic

Name: WDC-Admin
Description: Set by Savyint: Primary Admin persona, includes the Final Review Approval role

Name: WDC-CommodityManager
Description: Set by Savyin: Used primarily to track Commodity Managers in user reports. Commodity Manager reviews are limited to users in this group

Name: WDC-Finance
Description: Set by Savyint: Correlates to the Finance RDO, which includes the Financial Viability topic

Name: WDC-InfoSec
Description: Set by Savyint: Correlates to the InfoSec RDO, which includes the Information Security topic

Name: WDC-ITAdmin
Description: Set by Savyint: Primary IT Admin persona

Name: WDC-NonNetworkApproval
Description: Set by Savyint: Users in this group map to the Non-Network Approval user group

Name: WDC-Privacy
Description: Set by Savyint: Correlates to the Privacy RDO, which includes the Data Privacy and Artificial Intelligence topics

Name: WDC-Requester
Description: Set by Savyint: Basic Requestor persona

Name: WDC-Sales
Description: Set by Savyint: Basic Seller persona

Name: WDC-Sustainability
Description: Set by Savyint: Correlates to the Sustainability RDOs, which includes Environmental, Social & Governance and Responsible Minerals topics

Name: WDC-Tax
Description: Set by Savyint: Correlates to the W8 Review user group

Name: WDC-TPMO
Description: Set by Savyint: Correlates to the TPMO Governance user group

Name: WDC-Trade
Description: Set by Savyint: Correlates to the Trade RDOs

Name: WDC-UserAdmin
Description: Set by Savyint: Primary User Admin persona

Name: WDC-VendorMaster
Description: Set by Savyint: Correlates to the SMO group
